  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 14
  title: "B\xE1o c\xE1o th\xED nghi\u1EC7m #2"
  category: 4
  content: "\u0110\xE3 c\xF3 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi t\u1EF1 nguy\u1EC7n th\u1EED thu\u1ED1c,
    m\u1EE9c gi\xE1 \u0111\u01B0a ra l\xE0 30,000$. M\u1EE5c \u0111\xEDch l\u1EA7n
    th\u1EED nghi\u1EC7m n\xE0y l\xE0 ki\u1EC3m tra m\u1EE9c \u0111\u1ED9 t\u01B0\u01A1ng
    th\xEDch c\u1EE7a thu\u1ED1c l\xEAn con ng\u01B0\u1EDDi. \u0110\u1ED1i t\u01B0\u1EE3ng
    th\u1EED nghi\u1EC7m sau v\xE0i ng\xE0y th\u1EED nghi\u1EC7m c\xF3 tri\u1EC7u
    ch\u1EE9ng suy gi\u1EA3m \xFD th\u1EE9c, c\u01A1 b\u1EAFp b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u
    ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n m\u1EA5t ki\u1EC3m so\xE1t, n\xF3i n\u0103ng l\u1EAFp b\u1EAFp."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
